    "## 7. Done — restart the EC2 Gradio app to load the new models\n",
    "\n",
    "After all uploads complete, SSH into the EC2 instance and restart the app:\n",
    "\n",
    "```bash\n",
    "pkill -f 'python.*app.py'\n",
    "cd ~/poet-app && nohup ~/poet-app/melancholic_poet_qlora/.venv/bin/python app.py > ~/app.log 2>&1 &\n",
    "```\n",
    "\n",
    "The demo will now compare:\n",
    "- **Base model** (no fine-tuning)\n",
    "- **A: Full fine-tune** (unconditional persona, moderate LR)\n",
    "- **B: QLoRA r=32 aggressive** (LR 1e-3, no system prompt)\n",
    "\n",
    "Toggle the system prompt off to test if the persona is truly baked in."
   ]
